{"tid":1029973,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子食物和份量- 注意! 🐰🌟","createTime":"2019-02-20T15:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T12:19:35.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c84ee97dd2a471c45b70ae686e4fa37cb974cf17","tid":1029973,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:20:00.000Z","msg":"根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</strong><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡😊<br />\n- 2湯匙-無限兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意：</span><em>24小時無限兔糧是沒問題，但如果牠只吃糧不吃乾草就要減少兔糧，因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</strong><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意：</span><em>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</strong><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙或以下)水果<br />\n<br />\n<strong>老兔(6歲以上)：</strong><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</strong><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多資訊：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet%2F&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n82LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=6511826a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/</a>"},{"pid":"12e7eecf06eb6e0a7f90d911028f1c3651cdd2ed","tid":1029973,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUJhRRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUJhRRC.png&h=bcd16d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兔子食物"},{"pid":"df95cc01d77021d7b158d6d860b26c153b57b835","tid":1029973,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4465e24031826e75b74647c39a47b81a3f913120","tid":1029973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c85095db6db4a35e9dd493f193c1361593f2f2","tid":1029973,"uid":59221,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"block左2 3樓果2條以為自己好好笑既柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bf2d8bd45967e49852754af10eed48a1f9bf60","tid":1029973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}